I NEED YOUR HELP 
TO GET OVER THE WALL. PUSH ME.

332
00:11:34,526 --> 00:11:36,528
- I'M THE PATHETIC ONE, BUSTER, 
NOT YOU.

333
00:11:36,528 --> 00:11:39,198
I TOTALLY FREAKED OUT IN FRONT 
OF THAT PROSECUTOR TODAY.

334
00:11:39,198 --> 00:11:42,159
LIKE A LITTLE GIRL 
IN A LITTLE DRESS--

335
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:45,245
LITTLE SADDLE SHOES, 
LITTLE PIGTAILS.

336
00:11:45,245 --> 00:11:47,539
- WOW, THAT DOES SOUND 
LIKE A LITTLE GIRL.

337
00:11:47,539 --> 00:11:49,792
COME ON, GET MY IRE UP.

338
00:11:49,792 --> 00:11:51,794
PUSH ME! 
[chuckles]

339
00:11:51,794 --> 00:11:53,754
OH.

340
00:11:55,464 --> 00:11:56,924
OH, THIS IS TURNING OUT

341
00:11:56,924 --> 00:11:58,300
TO BE MUCH MORE FUN 
THAN I'D HOPED.

342
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:59,844
[narrator] 
IT WAS FUN.

343
00:11:59,844 --> 00:12:01,636
BUT IT WASN'T 
MAKING HIM A BETTER SOLDIER.

344
00:12:01,636 --> 00:12:03,430
- PUSH ME HIGHER. 
[chuckles]

345
00:12:03,430 --> 00:12:05,474
OOH! 
I'LL DO IT.

346
00:12:06,641 --> 00:12:07,893
WHOO!

347
00:12:07,893 --> 00:12:09,478
[narrator] 
AND MICHAEL REPORTED

348
00:12:09,478 --> 00:12:10,771
TO HIS FATHER ABOUT

349
00:12:10,771 --> 00:12:12,564
HIS MEETING WITH THE PROSECUTOR.

350
00:12:12,564 --> 00:12:14,608
- PROSECUTOR OFFER YOU A DEAL? 
- THAT WAS NOT SAID.

351
00:12:14,608 --> 00:12:17,027
BUT, UH, MORE IMPORTANTLY, 
YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT IT SEEMS

352
00:12:17,027 --> 00:12:19,279
LIKE OSCAR'S ON HIS WAY OUT.

353
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:21,281
- REALLY?

354
00:12:21,281 --> 00:12:23,575
- YEAH. SO JUST SIT TIGHT, 
AND EVERYTHING SHOULD BE FINE.

355
00:12:25,119 --> 00:12:27,955
- WOW. HEY, BY THE WAY, 
I BROKE THIS THING. I--

356
00:12:27,955 --> 00:12:30,916
WHAT THE HELL IS IT ANYWAY? 
- THAT'S A BREAST PUMP, DAD.

357
00:12:30,916 --> 00:12:34,211
- OH. WELL, I DID NOT 
USE IT FOR THAT.

358
00:12:34,211 --> 00:12:35,670
[narrator] 
AND SO MICHAEL WENT

359
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:37,589
TO MEET THE PROSECUTOR.

360
00:12:37,589 --> 00:12:39,758
- I FELT OBLIGATED TO SHARE 
SOME PHOTOGRAPHS WITH YOU.

361
00:12:39,758 --> 00:12:42,052
I OBTAINED THESE FROM 
THE BLUTH COMPANY E-MAIL SERVER.

362
00:12:42,052 --> 00:12:44,554
- YOU TAPPED INTO OUR E-MAIL? 
THAT'S LEGAL?

363
00:12:44,554 --> 00:12:46,598
- I'M GOING FOR A HOT DING DONG.

364
00:12:46,598 --> 00:12:49,601
HOT DING DONG? 
YEAH?

365
00:12:49,601 --> 00:12:51,770
- MICHAEL, THIS IS 
A CLOSE-UP SATELLITE PHOTOGRAPH

366
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:53,397
OF THE IRAQI COUNTRYSIDE.

367
00:12:53,397 --> 00:12:55,941
SEE THIS LITTLE SERIES OF HILLS 
AROUND THAT STREAM?

368
00:12:55,941 --> 00:12:58,110
THOSE ARE BUNKERS. 
WE BELIEVE THAT THOSE BUNKERS...

369
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,320
CONTAIN WEAPONS 
OF MASS DESTRUCTION.

370
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,738
WE ALSO THINK THAT YOUR FATHER

371
00:13:01,738 --> 00:13:04,283
WAS BUILDING ON THAT LAND 
TO HIDE THEM.

372
00:13:04,283 --> 00:13:07,077
WHICH IS WHY THAT PHOTOGRAPH 
WAS ON HIS E-MAIL.

373
00:13:07,077 --> 00:13:09,830
- ARE YOU SERIOUS? 
