374
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,957
I WAS ONCE CALLED 
THE WORST AUDIENCE PARTICIPANT

375
00:13:11,957 --> 00:13:13,000
CIRQUE DU SOLEIL EVER HAD.

376
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,543
