377
00:13:14,543 --> 00:13:16,795
- I DID NOT FIND 
THEIR BUFFOONERY AMUSING.

378
00:13:16,795 --> 00:13:18,797
- ABOUT MY FATHER.

379
00:13:18,797 --> 00:13:21,466
- HE'S GUILTY, MICHAEL, 
OF MEDIUM TO HEAVY TREASON.

380
00:13:21,466 --> 00:13:23,635
