TO OSCAR.

391
00:13:42,696 --> 00:13:44,364
ANYTHING ELSE? 
- NO.

392
00:13:44,364 --> 00:13:45,866
OH. HEY, DID I TELL YOU?

393
00:13:45,866 --> 00:13:47,701
