MAKING A LUNCH DATE.

398
00:13:57,086 --> 00:13:59,129
- I THOUGHT YOU WERE 
SPENDING TIME WITH MAEBY.

399
00:13:59,129 --> 00:14:01,256
- YEAH. I'LL HAVE TO 
RESCHEDULE HER.

400
00:14:01,256 --> 00:14:03,258
BUT MOM ISN'T THE ONLY ONE 
"FINDING LOVE" WHERE SHE

401
00:14:03,258 --> 00:14:04,301
LEAST EXPECTS IT.

402
00:14:04,301 --> 00:14:05,427
HER WORDS.

403
00:14:05,427 --> 00:14:06,636
- WH-WHOA! 
FINDING LOVE--

404
00:14:06,636 --> 00:14:09,348
