WHERE, HERE?

405
00:14:09,348 --> 00:14:11,350
- YEAH, SHE WON'T 
SHUT UP ABOUT HIM.

406
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,851
SHE SAID "TINGLING," 
LIKE, 75 TIMES.

407
00:14:12,851 --> 00:14:14,478
- GETS ME TINGLING.

408
00:14:14,478 --> 00:14:18,023
AND, YOU KNOW, WITH OSCAR 
THERE'S TINGLING.

409
00:14:18,023 --> 00:14:19,524
- SHE SAID THOSE WORDS 
IN THIS HOUSE?

410
00:14:19,524 --> 00:14:22,611
- YEAH.

411
00:14:22,611 --> 00:14:24,404
